{"type": "article", "id": 2212, "title": "木制灯泡", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:39:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052222548tHL9Sir0zIOngMC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">如果把灯泡的玻璃罩子换成木头会是什么样？日本设计师 Ryosuke Fukusada 给你答案。他创作了一款木质照明灯，内置 LED 节能灯，卡口是铝制的，外面的灯罩则是经过日本传统木工—— ROKURO 切削技术加工而成，木质外壳被打磨得非常薄，当灯亮起来时，木质外壳的纹路会显现出来，美妙的透光性为我们带来惊喜。即便在白天不需要灯光时，它亦可以被看作是一款装饰物。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134926ReCMQohnjz17YOc4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134926HhwNQMYIUx5sf8JC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}